Research is the primary way in which intellectuals engage with one another, share information, and educate themselves about their interests.  The goal of research \b is \i learning\b0\i0 , so you don\rquote t need to know anything about your topic before you get started, but you do need to have curiosity!  Bruce Ballenger reminds us, \ldblquote Your curiosity must be the driving force behind your research\rdblquote  (24).  In other words, it\rquote s better to be genuinely interested in your topic than it is to be an \ldblquote expert\rdblquote  on it\emdash as you conduct research, \b you will build up authority\b0  on your subject.  \par
\par
This essay represents an important step in the research process.  Conducting good background research helps you \b understand the larger conversation \b0 about a problem or issue:\par
\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sl276\slmult1\f2\'b7\tab\f0 What is the social, political, and/or historical context of the problem or issue you\rquote ve selected?\par
\f2\'b7\tab\f0 Who are the stakeholders and important players?  What are their concerns and suggestions?  \par
\f2\'b7\tab\f0 What are the significant debates, and how might your perspective contribute something meaningful to the discussion?  \par
\f2\'b7\tab\f0 What solutions have already been tried?  Did they work or didn\rquote t they? Why?\par
\pard\li720\sl276\slmult1\par
\pard\sl276\slmult1 The types of sources I\rquote m asking you to find for this assignment are meant to help you answer these questions, orient you within the public discussion about this topic, and prepare you for academic research.\par
\par
You are welcome to choose almost any topic you like, as long as you have a \b genuine curiosity\b0  and \b specific interest\b0  in the subject, and as long as the topic can be approached from a social justice perspective.  \b Some topics are generally prohibited, but may be approved if you are interested in \ul perusing a new angle\ulnone\b0  (legalization of marijuana, gay marriage, abortion, capital punishment, sex trafficking, and public prayer are all generally prohibited topics.  Bleh).  \par
